service.tut.pori.contentanalysis

Class AbstractTaskDetails

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.tut.pori.http.ResponseData
      • service.tut.pori.contentanalysis.AbstractTaskDetails
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContentStorageCore.SynchronizationTaskDetails, FBFeedbackTaskDetails, FBSummarizationTaskDetails, FBTaskDetails, PhotoTaskDetails, TaskDetails, TwitterSummarizationTaskDetails, TwitterTaskDetails, VideoTaskDetails

    public abstract class AbstractTaskDetails
extends ResponseData
    The base class for task details (task workload). Contains basic members and functionality needed for task submission. Note: remember to define \@XmlRootElement(name=ELEMENT_NAME) for your inherited class

    Optional Elements

    • userId, missing if task is generated by the system, or the task is anonymous.
    • taskParameters. The parameters depend on the task in question. If the element is missing the back-ends should run back-end specific default operation.
    See Also:
    BackendStatusList
